DataElement.preferredName: Notification Plan Study Activity Repeat Quantity ISO21090.URG.INT.NONNEG.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: An activity that is intended to occur at some point in the course of a particular study that represents the communication of a message to a recipient. The number of times the planned activity occurs. NOTE(S): If the frequency is more than once a day, this is still interpreted per time, e.g. BID for 5 days is 10 repeats.
